item.title: Kelley Mack, ‘9-1-1’ and ‘The Walking Dead’ Actress, Dies At 33
item.description: Kelley Mack, an American TV actress who appeared in AMC’s “The Walking Dead,” “9-1-1” and “Chicago Med,” died on Aug. 2. She was 33. Her family reported in a statement that Mack died in her home
